org.apache.spark.mllib.stat.test

Class WelchTTest

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.mllib.stat.test.WelchTTest

  • public class WelchTTest
extends Object
    Performs Welch's 2-sample t-test. The null hypothesis is that the two data sets have equal mean. This test does not assume equal variance between the two samples and does not assume equal sample size.

    See Also:
    Welch's t-test (Wikipedia)
